    "description": "<br><br><br>&quot;Ascendance&quot; 是一款即时战略游戏，玩家将控制一个文明迈出向太空扩张的第一步。该游戏拥有庞大的游戏世界、深度文明模拟和实时太空战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生机勃勃的星系</h2>深度文明提供了丰富而动态的体验，让玩家能够驾驭构成文明的相互关联系统的复杂网络。政府部门、军队、太空机构、私营企业、殖民地、人口和角色都有助于让文明栩栩如生，带来独特而身临其境的体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大规模</h2>在庞大无缝的星系中，拥有数十个卫星和行星的广阔恒星系统。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/8e941b436db465e965b4ce700f453e90.poster.avif?t=1754618963\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/8e941b436db465e965b4ce700f453e90.webm?t=1754618963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/8e941b436db465e965b4ce700f453e90.mp4?t=1754618963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >飞船战斗</h2>飞船战斗以物理为基础，武器使用预测瞄准、单独模拟射弹和基于位置的伤害。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/d618e112feeb7f180059ab36bfb65365.poster.avif?t=1754618963\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/d618e112feeb7f180059ab36bfb65365.webm?t=1754618963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/d618e112feeb7f180059ab36bfb65365.mp4?t=1754618963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >巨大星系</h2>在拥有数千到数万颗恒星的星系中探索、殖民并与其他文明竞争。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/db40222b4413ce1f47dcff3fa43c3e87.poster.avif?t=1754618963\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/db40222b4413ce1f47dcff3fa43c3e87.webm?t=1754618963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/db40222b4413ce1f47dcff3fa43c3e87.mp4?t=1754618963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深度经济</h2>管理由供需关系驱动的深度经济，包括基于地点的生产和消费、货运、大量资源、生产链和市场交换。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/0f09067f52e86723284a31982db19f53.poster.avif?t=1754618963\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/0f09067f52e86723284a31982db19f53.webm?t=1754618963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/0f09067f52e86723284a31982db19f53.mp4?t=1754618963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内部政治</h2>当政党、有影响力的人物、商业利益和普通大众各自追求自己的利益时，您将在文明的内部政治中游刃有余。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275750/extras/03dff52640c3fedfe70ea76e10404f4d.avif?t=1754618963\" width=616 height=160 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种玩法</h2>场景、游戏设置和计划中的修改支持都将允许玩家按照自己的意愿定制和玩游戏。你可以建立一个充满先进文明的星系，也可以在没有超光速旅行的单一恒星系统中进行游戏。由于行星和星系没有限制，因此可以真正实现高度发展。开始时是统一的文明，还是拥有多个国家的分裂文明。在整个星系或狭小的太空区域内进行游戏。一切由你决定！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >便利性</h2>这款游戏将非常深奥，但我们的目标是让玩家尽可能容易上手。我们非常注重让游戏机制直观易懂，并为玩家提供简洁的用户界面。",
